text: John Bell (by 1508 – 1533/44), of Leominster, Herefordshire, was an English politician. He was a Member (MP) of the Parliament of England for Leominster in 1529. ==References== Category:16th-century deaths Category:English MPs 1529–1536 Category:People from Leominster Category:Year of birth uncertain
title: John Bell (MP for Leominster)
